\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12928801 GS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4068123\charrsid16738601 No, I - I don't remember a great deal at all about me mother and father, but after mother died -
 I - I - the pleasant memories I have, I have all pleasant memories actually, but the pleasantest I can always remember was Whitsuntide, when we had the Whitsuntide treats and we always used to look for him coming because he was always very generous was m
e father and he used to treat everybody around and that's what - that's one of the pleasant things, well everything was pleasant actually but that was one of the things that stood out at all.
