\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12928801 GS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4068123\charrsid16738601 Yes, always had to have porridge first you know but -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2698416 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4068123\charrsid16738601 What would you have after?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12928801 GS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4068123\charrsid16738601 Usually bread and jam.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2698416 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4068123\charrsid16738601 Anything to drink with it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12928801 GS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4068123\charrsid16738601 Tea.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2698416 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4068123\charrsid16738601 Did you have anything special on Sundays?
