Oh no. Unless it were bacon sometimes, we'd bacon and egg at Sunday morning as a rule - as a rule. Yes, but they didn't have it every morning like they do here.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2698416 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4068123\charrsid16738601 Would it be Saturday as well or just Sunday?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12928801 GS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4068123\charrsid16738601 I just don't remember. Probably - but we were - I worked Saturday you know. We worked Saturday mornings so it would be a -
