\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2698416 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4068123\charrsid16738601 You had meat nearly every day at dinner time?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12928801 GS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4068123\charrsid16738601 Always something. Or fish.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2698416 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4068123\charrsid16738601 What about teas during the week?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12928801 GS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4068123\charrsid16738601 Well - always very plain. Plain. Bread and our own made jam always. We never knew what it was to buy a jar of jam. And - a }{\rtlch\fcs1 
\af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6118986\charrsid16738601 h}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4068123\charrsid16738601 am or cheese or - or lettuce, garden stuff, always something - you know - home grown or something.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2698416 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4068123\charrsid16738601 Your grandfather would grow lettuces?
