\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2698416 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4068123\charrsid16738601 He didn't have a frame?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12928801 GS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4068123\charrsid16738601 Oh no, no, just lettuce I can remember.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2698416 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4068123\charrsid16738601 Your grandfather would always be back home for teatime?
