\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2698416 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4068123\charrsid16738601 And all four of you would sit down to it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12928801 GS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4068123\charrsid16738601 Well I used to come later. You see, I - I didn't get home, I worked out of Undercliffe and -
