\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2698416 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4068123\charrsid16738601 Your auntie and grandma made all your bread?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12928801 GS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4068123\charrsid16738601 Oh yes, yes, always.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2698416 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4068123\charrsid16738601 She made her own jam, do you remember her bottling fruit or vegetables?
