 man, I can see him now. Yes, he used to get - bad tempered and - you know, he - he - he wasn't - he wasn't very - that was only one of them that - but I knew all the others but we wouldn't have dared to - sort of - you know, say anything back, only
 Miss Dene that lived next door to me because - I knew her so well you know, yes, and -
